The '''Sunflower''' is a [[Flowers|flower]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Sunflower Seeds]] after 8 days.

Harvesting a sunflower will drop 1 Sunflower, and 0-2 [[Sunflower Seeds]]. The total seed drop often numbers around 75% to 90% of the number of sunflowers harvested.

