==Bundles==
Sunflower is used in the {{Bundle|dye||y}} and is one of the options for the {{Bundle|garden||y}}.

==Recipes==
Sunflower is not used in any recipes.

==Artisan Goods==
Note that the game does not consider [[Oil]] to be an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]], so it does not benefit from the [[Farming#Farming Skill|Artisan Profession]].
