==Tailoring==
Sunflower is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a dyeable {{name|Long Dress|link=Tailoring{{!}}Long Dress|class=inline}}. It is a yellow dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the yellow dye pot at Emily's and Haley's house for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
Sunflower is not used in any [[quests]].

==Notes==
*If placed within proper range of a [[Bee House#Range|Bee House]] (5 squares in any cardinal direction), a Sunflower will cause the [[Honey]] produced to become more profitable.

